    <stitle>International&#174; T 444E Diesel Engine Service, Model Year 1994 - 1998 - MANIFOLDS - Installation - Left
        Exhaust Manifold
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="1">
        <title>Left Exhaust Manifold</title>
        <figure id="f1200307" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figeg3/eg3304.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="328px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" box="yes"/>
            <caption>Installing the Left Exhaust Manifold</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Exhaust Manifold</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Bolt</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Apply Never-Seez&#174; to the threads of the manifold bolts.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the left exhaust manifold (with gasket, if required) and eight mounting bolts.
                Tighten the bolts in the specified sequence to the special torque value.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect the exhaust manifold flange to the turbocharger exhaust tube. Tighten the bolts to
                the special torque value.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
